SETTING: A bright modern kitchen. White shaker cabinets, metro-tiled splashback, gas hob with two simmering pots. A tablet propped against a cookbook stand. A child's drawing on the fridge. Morning light from a window above the sink.
CAMERA: Shot from across the kitchen island at standing eye level. 50mm lens equivalent. Shallow depth of field — background softly blurred, subject pin-sharp. Natural colour grading.
