SETTING: A small independent café interior. Worn wooden tables, warm pendant lighting overhead, a handwritten chalkboard menu mounted on the exposed brick wall behind him. On his table: a flat white in a ceramic cup, a half-eaten pastry on a small plate, the open laptop. Other customers are visible but out of focus — a woman alone reading a paperback to one side, two people mid-conversation at another table. The laptop screen reflects faintly in the window glass beside him.
OUTSIDE: Through the café window, a city street in soft depth of field — bicycles locked to a railing, a bus partially visible, pedestrians passing. Overcast urban daylight from outside contrasts gently with the warm interior light.
CAMERA: Shot from the table directly opposite at seated eye level, as if taken by someone sitting across the café. 50mm equivalent. Shallow depth of field — subject and immediate table sharp, background and other customers softly blurred. The man is clearly distinct from the table, chair, and window behind him — visible separation on all sides.
STYLE: Candid editorial photography. Realistic skin texture. Fine natural film grain — not digital noise. True-to-life colours, no colour grading filters. No AI smoothing, no plastic skin, no merging of subject with furniture or background.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writi