" dir="auto" data-turn-id="e74065cb-ee74-4625-9353-e05b4f4011a9" data-testid="conversation-turn-9" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)" style="scroll-margin-top: -540px;"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="e74065cb-ee74-4625-9353-e05b4f4011a9" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">SUBJECT: A couple in their early-to-mid 30s in a vintage open-top car on a coastal road. The woman is driving — one hand on the wheel, the other resting on the gear stick, wearing large sunglasses and a silk headscarf tied under her chin. The man is in the passenger seat, arm draped along the back of the seat, head turned toward the view. Both are clearly distinct from the car interior — visible separation between their bodies and the seats, door panels, and dashboard.VEHICLE: A classic vintage car, cream bodywork, tan leather seats, minimal dashboard detail. Convertible, roof fully down. The car is mid-motion on the road — not static.SETTING: A dramatic winding coastal road. The cliff drops steeply to the ocean far below on one side. Rocky outcrops and dry coastal scrub line the roadside. The road curves away in both directions with no other vehicles visible. Sun-bleached patches on the road surface.LIGHT &amp; SKY: Golden hour. The sun sits low on the horizon directly ahead of them, casting warm directional light across the scene. The sky is deep gold fading to pale blue. Long shadows stretch behind the car.CAMERA: Shot from slightly above and behind the car, as if from a following vehicle or drone at low altitude. The car fills the lower two-thirds of the frame. 1:1 square crop. The road and cliff edge frame the composition naturally.STYLE: Candid travel editorial photography. Realistic skin and material textures. Fine natural film grain — not digital noise. True-to-life warm colour grading. No AI smoothing, no plastic skin, no merging of figures with car interior. Subjects fully separated from background and vehicle surfaces.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg x